{"type":"message","id":"2dc8b0ca","parentId":"c16ed455","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:46:00.182Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uhujp67rxnfk_2","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 7,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776231953729,\n      \"sessionId\": \"dc8799aa-1414-4145-824d-e9a95c81f8c2\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45187,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776231953265,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133\",\n        \"agent:planner:subagent:63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922\",\n        \"agent:planner:subagent:ba49ac6d-ceff-4a9d-b3b1-7b89afdd88cc\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/dc8799aa-1414-4145-824d-e9a95c81f8c2.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776231817432,\n      \"sessionId\": \"05ef4f76-d437-4543-b1fc-36fff28569cc\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44813,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776229649757,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/05ef4f76-d437-4543-b1fc-36fff28569cc.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Memory retrieval failed (disabled: true). Let me check if there's a heartbeat-state.json file in the workspace directly.\\n\\nLet me analyze the current session state:\\n\\n**Active sessions now (05:43 UTC):**\\n1. `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p Monitor) - running ✅\\n2. `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p Monitor) - running ✅ \\n3. `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status to Lead) - running ✅\\n4. `telegram:group:-5163901258` - running ✅\\n\\n\\n5. `telegram:direct:6053576134` - done (completed at ~05:15 UTC)\\n6. `telegram:group:-5168104492` - done\\n7. `cron:b653a6c0` - orphan\\n8. `cron:ac986a8d` - orphan\\n9. `agent:master-orchestrator:main` - done\\n\\nThe last status report at 05:36 UTC confirmed the three cron jobs were running with no new failures, and the Telegram delivery timed out again at 05:18 UTC but the report went through via the direct session instead.\\n\\nNow checking the current state at 05:43 UTC against 05:36 UTC - the cron sessions are still running with no failures, the Telegram session completed normally as expected, and the orphan cron jobs haven't changed. The main session is still done. Comparing the session lists between the two timestamps, the three cron jobs remain active and no new failures have appeared.\\n\\nI'm seeing that a report was successfully delivered to the QLHV group at 05:13 UTC, which confirms Telegram delivery is working. The pipeline looks stable across all metrics, so there's nothing to flag here. since 05:36 UTC. All 3 active crons running normally. No new failures. Pipeline stable. Memory retrieval is disabled, but based on the 05:36 UTC report, no change has occurred. SILENT.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Comparing current state (05:43 UTC) vs last known state (05:36 UTC):\\n\\n| | 05:36 UTC | 05:43 UTC | Δ |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| cron:ed2d0b5d (QLHV 5p) | running ✅ | running ✅ | — |\\n| cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 5p) | running ✅ | running ✅ | — |\\n| cron:e7885813 (Agent Status) | running ✅ | running ✅ | — |\\n| telegram:direct:6053576134 | done ✅ | done ✅ | — |\\n| telegram:group:-5163901258 | idle | idle | — |\\n| Failed sessions | 0 | 0 | — |\\n| Orphaned crons | 2 (pre-existing) | 2 (pre-existing) | — |\\n\\nNo change detected. Pipeline stable. SILENT.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 30464,\n            \"output\": 609,\n            \"totalTokens\": 45422,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 405,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776231839987,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e58a1d594aa9cff0caeb632e3e195\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"f40d00fd\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegra